353
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:26,900
I didn't expect the previous Chief would have that kind of a past.

354
00:29:26,900 --> 00:29:30,790
A single general achieves fame on the rotting bones of tens of thousands.

355
00:29:31,380 --> 00:29:34,300
Who set a game here?

356
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:36,020
This is so confusing.

357
00:29:36,020 --> 00:29:38,960
I also don't know if this is just the beginning

358
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:41,750
