359
00:29:41,750 --> 00:29:43,640
Discard this chessboard and go.

360
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:48,970
- This chess game looks like today's situation. 
 - Why do you say so?

361
00:29:48,970 --> 00:29:52,990
These two white and black chess pieces can be compared to Shangguan Hui and Chief Xiao.

362
